pack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4w5","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17372,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/four-things-happiness-misery\/","url_meta":{"origin":17365,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Living: Four things part of happiness, misery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFour things are part of happiness: a righteous spouse, a spacious dwelling, a righteous neighbor, and a comfortable mount. Four things are part of misery: a bad neighbor, a bad spouse, a restrictive dwelling,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21585,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/12\/love-allah-truthful-trustworthy\/","url_meta":{"origin":17365,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: If you love Allah, be truthful, trustworthy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Qurad reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is pleased to love Allah and His Messenger, or to be loved by Allah and His Messenger, let him be truthful when he speaks, let him fulfill the trust to whom it is due, and let\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/14\/two-neighbors-first-judge\/","url_meta":{"origin":17365,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Two neighbors first to dispute on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong the first disputants on the Day of Resurrection will be two neighbors.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 17372 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":586,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/02\/27\/be-kind-to-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":17365,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: Be kind to neighbors, regardless of religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: We were with Abdullah ibn Amr while his servant prepared to distribute a sheep. Abdullah said, \u201cYoung man, when you are finished, then begin with our Jewish neighbor.\u201d A man said, \u201cJewish? May Allah correct you!\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cI heard the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/23\/best-neighbor-companion\/","url_meta":{"origin":17365,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: The best neighbor is best to his neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best companion to Allah is the best to his companions, and the best neighbor to Allah is the best to his neighbors.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1944 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/13\/malice-neighbors\/","url_meta":{"origin":17365,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Malice: Believers are not malicious to neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is not a believer whose neighbor is not safe from his malevolence.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak \u2018ala\u0301 al-S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323ayn 7300 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0